hiveArticle.title: FoodPhotography - Rajasthani Thali
hiveArticle.body:
I went to have dinner to Rajdhani yesterday where they serve authentic Rajasthani Thalis. They have served around 35 varieties of food including Wheat bread, Rice, different kind of pulses, etc.. 

![](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmXBsFkmuK2JtbNn8GE83W52akb34ZSQianCJi7CXdEwAP/image.png)

![](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmXs5MBjSVMhiijAu3gPz3Vsoz5aC6zCb83UAwfqrtR8rd/image.png)

### Camera : Nokia 6
